{"tid":714121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無綫TVBI傳裁40%人手","createTime":"2018-06-23T12:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T08:13:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":71,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"80cc7c42bdf99079b4a5cd1298bba0ea5e97dc36","tid":714121,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:09:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180623/20428763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F20428763&d=FiAKgoml5Zz3hpx%2Bxsr10cPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=a2a449f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180623%2F20428763&h=55b4b121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180623/20428763</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月23日 <br />\n<br />\n無綫TVBI傳裁40%人手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180623/large/23ec2p9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180623%2Flarge%2F23ec2p9.jpg&h=2a4c4949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有指無綫將裁減TVBI的技術人員，未知會否涉及藝員。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無綫近日傳出裁員，「方以文睇電視喇喂」facebook page昨爆出裁員消息，指受影響部門包括TVBI和Broadcast Operation Department，收「大信封」的人數更佔部門總人數10%。<br />\n<br />\n據知，主要受影響的TVBI，保守估計約有逾百名員工，最近開除兩位經理級職員外，未來還會裁減40%人手。TVBI主要負責海外市場業務，包括過往發行錄影帶及影碟，以及大型節目用衞星傳送訊號到海外，但現在的TVB anywhere經寬頻傳送，因此TVBI的衞星直播技術人員成被裁對象。對於TVBI將裁減40%人手，TVB企業傳訊部對外事務科昨回應傳媒說：「不作回應。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：魯吉  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n羅霖被拖百萬酬金<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n袁文傑拍劇傷尾指"},{"pid":"a2821bf2ce04a5a49c8590eec76fc4171c9cae0c","tid":714121,"uid":54337,"like":85,"dislike":2,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/201640_644afba3ac1b252d769952d02eea84e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F201640_644afba3ac1b252d769952d02eea84e7.jpg&h=c4290f62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cb1dd3e9b5d4d094f7432edbcc42d2435c67444","tid":714121,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:25:04.000Z","msg":"喜氣洋洋"},{"pid":"0618cde9231af927dbc584b54af8d0c318f5bb10","tid":714121,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0f025a223a15395050a70c7a346a41a463e3f0","tid":714121,"uid":2054,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/184142_116e4ab2cc9bd5df406a214afa33b89f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F184142_116e4ab2cc9bd5df406a214afa33b89f.png&h=88fb0d65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9818c38a3b0689fe8915be40d6e809e217b6f7a","tid":714121,"uid":17646,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:31:14.000Z","msg":"TVBI邊有藝員咩<br />\n全部都係簽TVB"},{"pid":"76e6a16b2b4c427a0d10390801d96cbe67e92777","tid":714121,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:31:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>TVBI邊有藝員呀<br />\n全部都係簽TVB</blockquote>"},{"pid":"176ccb7bb7ea78dfd86e5e6b3791473acc837a36","tid":714121,"uid":91633,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T12:31:27.000Z","msg":"越黎越似ATV既後步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9a2368f4c0f679427a656a01fc44cd74ef0eb3","tid":714121,"uid":17646,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"176ccb7bb7ea78dfd86e5e6b3791473acc837a36","tid":714121,"uid":91633,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0